</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><term class="- topic/term " outputclass="no_quotes">Indicates a warning concerning operations that may lead to death or injury to persons if not performed correctly. To use the machine safely, always pay attention to these warnings.</term> 
