</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><term class="- topic/term " outputclass="no_quotes">Indicates a clarification of an operation or contains additional explanations for a procedure. Reading these notes is highly recommended.</term> 
